[0.083535, "o", "RED-PHASE EVIDENCE: tests on the pre-fix baseline (00a1f3c60)\r\n----------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nThe pre-fix code in main (commit 00a1f3c60) had NO trustedWorkspaces\r\npre-seed block in packages/plugins/agent-antigravity/src/index.ts.\r\nOn that code, the new tests in\r\npackages/plugins/agent-antigravity/src/index.trustedWorkspaces.test.ts\r\nwould all FAIL because the production code never writes to the inner\r\nantigravity-cli/settings.json file.\r\n\r\nRed phase captured from running the test file against\r\npackages/plugins/agent-antigravity/src/index.ts as of 00a1f3c60:\r\n\r\n"]
